timeshift (1.6.2) trusty; urgency=medium

  * New option to clone current system
  
  * Fixed: Restore fails with Xterm terminal

  * Fixed: Install libgee2 on ArchLinux instead of libgee
  
  * Snapshot date will be displayed in 12-hour fomat

  * Removed dependency on 'du' utility
  
  * Improved first snapshot size estimation

  * Added tooltip descriptions for columns in snapshot list

  * Tag column in snapshot list will display single letters for each tag
  
